data.description: Welcome to this stunning home offering an expansive 4524 square feet of meticulously crafted living space. Boasting 5 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, and a finished basement with a convenient walk-up outside entrance, this residence redefines comfort and elegance.  The attached  2-car garage features built in storage.  Move in worry free with a new roof installed in 2022, ensuring both functionality and durability. Noteworthy upgrades include a recently installed downstairs HVAC system in 2022 and an upstairs HVAC system replaced in 2020, guaranteeing year-round comfort and efficiency. There is a radon mitigation system already installed and the seller is offering a one year home warranty for peace of mind.  The exterior showcases a thoughtfully installed sprinkler system in 2020, providing ease in maintaining the lush landscaping, while a new fence in the rear yard, added in 2022, ensures privacy and security. Entertaining is a delight as the pool table and exercise equipment will convey, making this home an entertainer's dream.  Step inside to find a pristine interior resembling a model home, adorned with granite countertops and gleaming hardwood floors throughout. The layout includes a separate office, living room, dining room, and a cozy family room, each exuding its unique charm and functionality.  The primary bedroom is a luxurious retreat, featuring a delightful sitting room and a fireplace, creating a serene ambiance. A walk-in closet offers ample storage, while the primary bath boasts a separate shower and tub, along with double sinks, providing a spa-like experience at home.  Convenience meets luxury with an upstairs laundry room that has been remodeled, complete with front load washer and dryer that will convey with the property. The flooring matches the hardwoods upstairs but it ceramic.  Enjoy the outdoors on the maintenance-free deck in the rear or unwind on the inviting front porch, adding to the home's charming appeal. The brick front facade further enhances the exterior's timeless elegance.  This home encapsulates the perfect blend of sophistication, functionality, and comfort, offering an unparalleled living experience in every aspect. Close to downtown, shopping, the hospital and the VRE.
